{"tid":174763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"小學生作文","createTime":"2017-03-27T05:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T05:46:06.000Z","uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3828ff93fda396e498d7a12ef123cad5a5c04b","tid":174763,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"Write a composition about yourself<br />\n<br />\nMy name is Tom. I am from Hong Kong. I am a student. I am six years old.<br />\n<br />\nMy family lives in Center. My father is sixty-nine years old. My mother is fifty-one years old. I have a sister and a brother. The name of my sister is Rosa. She is a doctor. She is twenty-six years old. The name of my brother is Pedro. He is a student. He is thirteen years old. <br />\n<br />\nI live in an apartment. My address is 3225 Pine St. I live with my family.<br />\n<br />\nI like my classes. They are interesting. I like my classmates. They are friendly and helpful.<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe56a08dead09b3a9cc025c03fa766d4a247d1e4","tid":174763,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"俾個A+你"},{"pid":"4eb7abb53fa7eea9555733f545600ef0bfdb943c","tid":174763,"uid":90978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"Center<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02abd3b738845cda0649ef563da70ee6d3e430f","tid":174763,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"5*******<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23a2fd4a727cde174a2ee4039e739a092e351b1","tid":174763,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco